<OUTPUT_TEXT>Subject: Referral of Unresolved Customer Grievances for Further Investigation

Dear Team,

I hope this message finds you well. I am writing to bring to your attention several unresolved customer grievances that have been escalated to our department. Despite our best efforts, we have been unable to fully address these issues and believe they require further investigation from your team.

Please find below a summary of the grievances along with the relevant customer details:

1. Complaint: Delayed delivery of order #12345
   Customer Name: John Smith
   Contact Number: 555-123-4567

2. Complaint: Incorrect billing charges on account #67890
   Customer Name: Jane Doe
   Contact Number: 555-987-6543

3. Complaint: Defective product received under warranty claim #13579
   Customer Name: Alex Johnson
   Contact Number: 555-456-7890

We kindly request your prompt attention to these matters and would appreciate it if you could investigate and resolve them as soon as possible. Should you require any additional information or assistance from our end, please do not hesitate to reach out.

Thank you for your cooperation in addressing these unresolved grievances promptly.

Best regards,

[Your Name]
Senior Customer Service Representative</OUTPUT_TEXT>
